data.description: This charming home offers a spacious and open floor plan, perfect for entertaining friends and family. With 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, there is plenty of room for everyone to have their own space. As you enter the home, you will be greeted by wide crown molding and a detached fireplace, creating a cozy atmosphere throughout. The bonus room provides additional flexibility, whether you need a home office, playroom, or guest space. The fenced yard offers privacy and security for pets or outdoor activities. Additionally, the storage building provides ample space for all your belongings. Conveniently located close to schools, this home is ideal for families looking to settle down in a friendly neighborhood. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home.
